   <text>
      <body>
         <head type="date">
            <date>December 3, 1804</date>
         </head>
         <div type="entry" xml:id="lc.1804-12-03.01">
            <sp who="wc">
               <speaker>Clark</speaker>
               <ab>
                  <date>3rd 
              <hi rend="italic">December Monday 1804.</hi>
                  </date>
               </ab>
               <p>a fine morning    the after part of the day Cold &amp; windey   
          the wind from the N W.    The Father of the 
          <name type="native_nation" key="Mandan Indians">Mandan</name>who was killed Came and
          made us a present of Some Dried Simnens [
          <hi rend="italic">NB: Pumpkins</hi>] &amp; a little pemicon [
          <hi rend="italic">NB: pemitigon</hi>], we made him Some Small preasents for which he was
          much pleased</p>
            </sp>
         </div>
         <div type="entry" xml:id="lc.1804-12-03.02">
            <sp who="jo">
               <speaker>Ordway</speaker>
               <ab>
                  <date/>
               </ab>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Monday 3rd Decr</hi>.    cold &amp; windy.    the
          work carried on as usal.    commenced Setting up the pickets and bring pickets
          &amp;.C. &amp;.C.</p>
            </sp>
         </div>
